1274
01:47:43,606 --> 01:47:44,641
Anyway?

1275
01:47:44,726 --> 01:47:48,082
Are they ready to testify and 
tell the people the truth?

1276
01:47:49,726 --> 01:47:51,876
- Are you ready, Father? 
- Yes.

1277
01:47:53,366 --> 01:47:56,722
