or dead martyrs.

1310
01:52:25,206 --> 01:52:27,481
The uprising would have no cause.

1311
01:52:37,686 --> 01:52:42,555
Do you know? 
This time the soft is right.

1312
01:52:42,646 --> 01:52:45,922
Get rid of the causers.

1313
01:52:51,006 --> 01:52:54,043
Shameful expulsion from China.

1314
01:52:54,126 --> 01:52:56,082
Not ashamed, Father.

1315
01:52:56,166 --> 01:52:59,556
People will always remember 
that you told the truth yourself.

1316
01:52:59,646 --> 01:53:01,238
I hope so.

1317
01:53:11,606 --> 01:53:13,164
Ez Ho-San.

1318
01:53:20,126 --> 01:53:22,515
Now send us back to the village to 
be shot.

1319
01:53:22,606 --> 01:53:25,074
This is not an instruction. 
I'm trying to escape.

1320
01:53:25,166 --> 01:53:27,206
- I need their help. 
- How can we help?

1321
01:53:27,206 --> 01:53:29,276
I planned everything. 
Get in my car.

1322
01:53:29,326 --> 01:53:31,601
If we're lucky, we'll do it before ...

1323
01:53:37,446 --> 01:53:40,006
I just wanted to ask if you understand English.

1324
01:53:40,086 --> 01:53:43,362
No more questions now. 
Hurry up. I'll tell you everything later.

1325
01:54:02,366 --> 01:54:05,399
This was my last 
act that did not fit the Christian.

1326
01:54:11,166 --> 01:54:13,555
You can sit up now. 
Don't drown.

1327
01:54:14,661 --> 01:54:15,861
Sri Lanka.

1328
01:54:15,886 --> 01:54:19,720
I'm grateful they joined. 
I hope we have a safe journey.

1329
01:54:20,646 --> 01:54:22,238
Is he here by free will?

1330
01:54:22,326 --> 01:54:25,682
I'm just with Ho-San for the baby.

1331
01:54:25,766 --> 01:54:27,996
If we get to Hong Kong freely ...

1332
01:54:28,086 --> 01:54:29,804
we are getting married ...

1333
01:54:29,886 --> 01:54:32,081
just because of the baby.

1334
01:54:32,166 --> 01:54:34,202
Just to give the baby a name.

1335
01:54:35,061 --> 01:54:37,061
No...

1336
01:54:37,086 --> 01:54:40,317
There is more to it. 
I want to raise my son ...

1337
01:54:40,366 --> 01:54:42,197
"A fiamat"?

1338
01:54:42,246 --> 01:54:44,202
Our son ...

1339
01:54:44,286 --> 01:54:47,642
where parents are free to 
talk to their child.

1340
01:54:47,726 --> 01:54:51,685
You have to learn a lot from your father’s mistakes.

1341
01:54:56,246 --> 01:54:59,363
He was a strong opponent, Ho-San.

1342
01:54:59,406 --> 01:55:03,035
I hope 
he will be just as strong as an ally.

1343
01:55:03,086 --> 01:55:05,805
I'm trying to be like that.

1344
01:55:05,886 --> 01:55:10,562
One day, I 
suffered a lifelong disappointment.

1345
01:55:10,646 --> 01:55:14,719
I saw my mother 
and father shot in a chapel ...

1346
01:55:14,806 --> 01:55:16,717
just because they went to pray.

1347
01:55:18,701 --> 01:55:20,701
Oh, no.

1348
01:55:20,726 --> 01:55:23,286
After all my years in China ...

1349
01:55:23,366 --> 01:55:26,517
