1353
01:55:48,406 --> 01:55:50,840
They follow us.

1354
01:55:50,966 --> 01:55:52,922
This is the killer of Chung Ren, my mother and father.

1355
01:55:54,926 --> 01:55:58,316
Forgive me for a moment. 
I'll be right back.

1356
01:56:11,166 --> 01:56:15,956
I have now performed my first act 
as a returned Christian.

1357
01:56:27,686 --> 01:56:29,881
See how well I designed it?

1358
01:56:29,966 --> 01:56:32,355
The guards on the communist side of the bridge 
will think ...

1359
01:56:32,406 --> 01:56:34,283
