1385
01:59:18,126 --> 01:59:20,686
Ho-ban-yon.

1386
01:59:20,766 --> 01:59:22,324
Ho what?

1387
01:59:24,606 --> 01:59:26,517
Ho-ban-yon.

1388
01:59:28,686 --> 01:59:32,838
